ro.uaic.info.optdist.internal

Class Optional

  • java.lang.Object
    • ro.uaic.info.optdist.internal.Optional
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OptionalInterface

    @Component
public class Optional
extends Object
implements OptionalInterface
    Stores all data relevant to an optional.

    Specifically, this data is the optional's name, year, semester, current enrolled students, capacity, ID and admission grade.
